      {
        "inline": {
          "part_type": "Heading",
          "text": [
            "هَذَا آخِرُ كِتَابِ الْقَضَايَا وَ الْأَحْكَامِ مِنْ كِتَابِ الْكَافِي وَ يَتْلُوهُ كِتَابُ الْأَيْمَانِ وَ النُّذُورِ وَ الْكَفَّارَاتِ إِنْ شَاءَ اللَّهُ تَعَالَى"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "en.hubeali": [
              "This is the end of the Book of the judgement and the ruling from the book Al Kafi, and it would be followed by the book of oaths, and the vows, and the expiations, Allah<sup>azwj</sup> the Exalted Willing."
            ]
          }
        },
        "part_type": "Heading"
